[[File:酉の市Torinoichi000.jpg|thumb|{{ill|Tori-no-Ichi|ja|酉の市|1=Tori-no-Ichi}}の{{ill|Kumade|ja|熊手}}]]
'''Ōtori Shrine''' (大鷲神社, also pronounced Ōwashi Shrine) refers to a name for various {{ill|Shinto shrine|ja|神社}} across Japan. These shrines are part of the {{ill|Ōtori faith|ja|大鳥信仰}}, with {{ill|Ōtori Taisha|ja|大鳥大社|1=Ōtori taisha}} as their main shrine. Many are related to other shrines with similar names, such as {{ill|Ōtori Shrine (disambiguation)|ja|大鳥神社 (曖昧さ回避)}}, {{ill|Washi Shrine (disambiguation)|ja|鷲神社 (曖昧さ回避)}}, and {{ill|Washi-no-Miya Shrine (disambiguation)|ja|鷲宮神社 (曖昧さ回避)}}. Several are also widely known for hosting {{ill|Tori-no-Ichi|ja|酉の市|1=Tori-no-Ichi}} festivals. There are seven such shrines officially recognized as religious corporations nationwide.

For related terms, see {{ill|Ōtori Shrine (disambiguation)|ja|大鳥神社 (曖昧さ回避)}}, {{ill|Washi Shrine (disambiguation)|ja|鷲神社 (曖昧さ回避)}}, {{ill|Washi-no-Miya Shrine (disambiguation)|ja|鷲宮神社 (曖昧さ回避)}}, and {{ill|Ame-no-Hiwashi Shrine (disambiguation)|ja|日鷲神社 (曖昧さ回避)}}.

* {{ill|Ōtori Shrine (Tsukuba)|ja|大鷲神社 (つくば市)}} - Located in Tedegaki, Tsukuba City, Ibaraki Prefecture.
* {{ill|Ōtori Shrine (Ichikawa)|ja|大鷲神社 (市川市)}} - Located in Takaya, Ichikawa City, Chiba Prefecture.
* {{ill|Ōtori Shrine (Ichihara)|ja|大鷲神社 (市原市)}} - Located in Yanagihara, Ichihara City, Chiba Prefecture.
* {{ill|Ōtori Shrine (Narita)|ja|大鷲神社 (成田市)}} - Located in Kitahatori, Narita City, Chiba Prefecture.
* {{ill|Ōtori Shrine (Sakae)|ja|大鷲神社 (栄町)}} - Located in Anjō, Sakae Town, Inba District, Chiba Prefecture.
* {{ill|Ōtori Shrine (Shisui)|ja|大鷲神社 (酒々井町)}} - Located in Kamiiwahashi, Shisui Town, Inba District, Chiba Prefecture.
* {{ill|Ōtori Shrine (Adachi)|ja|大鷲神社 (足立区)}} - Located in Hanahata, Adachi Ward, Tokyo. Known as the origin of Tori-no-Ichi.
* Ōtori Shrine - Located in Miyamachi, Fuchū City, Tokyo. A subsidiary shrine of {{ill|Ōkunitama Shrine|ja|大國魂神社}}.
* Ōtori Shrine - Located in Makane-chō, Minami Ward, Yokohama City, Kanagawa Prefecture. Consolidated into the precincts of a {{ill|Konpira Shrine|ja|金刀比羅神社}} (see {{ill|Konpira and Ōtori Shrine|ja|金刀比羅・大鷲神社}}).

