For related terms, see {{ill|Ōtori Shrine (disambiguation)|ja|大鳥神社 (曖昧さ回避)|12=draft}}, {{ill|Washi Shrine (disambiguation)|ja|鷲神社 (曖昧さ回避)|12=draft}}, {{ill|Washi-no-Miya Shrine (disambiguation)|ja|鷲宮神社 (曖昧さ回避)|12=draft}}, and {{ill|Ame-no-Hiwashi Shrine (disambiguation)|ja|日鷲神社 (曖昧さ回避)|12=draft}}.

