* {{ill|Ōtori Shrine (Tsukuba)|ja|大鷲神社 (つくば市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtori Shrine (Tsukuba)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Tedegaki, Tsukuba City, Ibaraki Prefecture. * {{ill|Ōtori Shrine (Ichikawa)|ja|大鷲神社 (市川市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtori Shrine (Ichikawa)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Takaya, Ichikawa City, Chiba Prefecture. * {{ill|Ōtori Shrine (Ichihara)|ja|大鷲神社 (市原市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtori Shrine (Ichihara)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Yanagihara, Ichihara City, Chiba Prefecture. * {{ill|Ōtori Shrine (Narita)|ja|大鷲神社 (成田市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtori Shrine (Narita)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Kitahatori, Narita City, Chiba Prefecture. * {{ill|Ōtori Shrine (Sakae)|ja|大鷲神社 (栄町)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtori Shrine (Sakae)|qq=}} - Located in Anjō, Sakae Town, Inba District, Chiba Prefecture. * {{ill|Ōtori Shrine (Shisui)|ja|大鷲神社 (酒々井町)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtori Shrine (Shisui)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Kamiiwahashi, Shisui Town, Inba District, Chiba Prefecture. * {{ill|Ōtori Shrine (Adachi Ward)|lt=Ōtori Shrine (Adachi Ward)|lt=Ōtori Shrine (Adachi)|ja|大鷲神社 (足立区)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtori Shrine (Adachi)|qq=}} - Located in Hanahata, Adachi Ward, Tokyo. Known as the origin of Tori-no-Ichi. * Ōtori Shrine - Located in Miyamachi, Fuchū City, Tokyo. A subsidiary shrine of [[:en:Ōkunitama Shrine|Ōkunitama Shrine]]. * Ōtori Shrine - Located in Makane-chō, Minami Ward, Yokohama City, Kanagawa Prefecture. Consolidated into the precincts of a {{ill|Kotohira shrines|lt=Kotohira shrines|lt=Konpira Shrine|ja|金刀比羅神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Konpira Shrine|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} (see {{ill|Konpira and Ōtori Shrine|ja|金刀比羅・大鷲神社|1=Konpira and Ōtori Shrine|qq=draf